Please find the following Documentation for Covid19 App

We have three Main Headers in our Application.
1. Dashboard : Displays all State Records of Covid-19 Affected States. Upon Clicking Drop Down you can view the Covid-19 records City-Wise for that respective state.
2. Latest News : This Tab displays the latest On Going news related to Covid-19. 
   2a. Admin can login using the following credentials to add new news Items
          "username" : "admin"
          "password" : "admin"
   2b. Normal User can view the News Items published by the admin.
3. Precautions Tab is a static component with displays all the Precautions that should be taken.


Login session is being maintained which does not cause the user to logout while refreshing Window or navigating to any other Tab within the App. 
